::Prowl::

Prowl blinks as Iron Raptor jumps backward into the wall. He nearly chuckles, 
looking at her.

Prowl's spark jumps as he hears her speak. He loved her voice, even in this 
situation. His eyes look her over, noting that she was not in top condition.

"Its me," he says in responce to her question, taking out the other cloaking 
device from his storage compartment.

"Here, catch," he says, throwing the device to her, "Its a cloaking device. 
You'll be able to see me once its activated."

Prowl pauses, looking once again at Iron Raptor. "Are you allright?" he asks, 
concern in his voice.
